quran[55]{c,v,t}:
  82,1,When/if the sky/space split/cracked/cleaved
  82,2,And when/if the stars/planets scattered/spread
  82,3,And when/if the seas/oceans burst/over flowed
  82,4,And when/if the graves/burial places are scattered/over thrown
  82,5,A self knew what it advanced/preceded and delayed
  82,6,"You, you the human/mankind, what has deceived/tempted you with (from) your Lord, the honoured/generous"
  82,7,"Who created you, so He straightened you, so He balanced/adjusted you"
  82,8,In any shape/picture what He willed/intended He assembled/composed you
  82,9,"No but, rather you lie/deny/falsify with the religion"
  82,10,And that truly (We are) on you protectors/observers (E)
  82,11,"Honoured/generous , writing/ordering"
  82,12,They (the angels) know what you make/do
  82,13,That truly the righteous/charitable (are) in (E) blessing/goodness
  82,14,And that truly the debauchers/corrupters (are) in (E) Hell
  82,15,They roast/suffer (from) it (in) the Judgment Day/Resurrection Day
  82,16,And they are not from it with (being) absent/hidden
  82,17,And what made you know/informed you what (is) the Judgment Day/Resurrection Day
  82,18,Then what made you know/informed you what the Judgment Day/Resurrection Day (is)
  82,19,"A day/time a self does not own/possess to a self a thing, and the matter/affair/order/command (on) that day (is) to God"
  83,1,Calamity/scandal to the ones giving insufficient or deficient measures
  83,2,"Those who if they took by measure or weight for themselves on (from) the people, they fulfill/complete (the measure or weight)"
  83,3,"And if they measured/weighed for them or they weighed/measured for them , they reduce/decrease (cheat)"
  83,4,Do those not think/assume that they are being resurrected/revived
  83,5,To a great day/time
  83,6,A day/time the people stand to the creations all together`s/(universes`) Lord
  83,7,No but that truly the debauchers`/corrupters` Book/judgment (is) in (E) Sijjin
  83,8,And what made you know/informed you what (is) Sijjin
  83,9,A written/branded/inscribed Book
  83,10,Calamity/scandal (on) that day to the liars/deniers/falsifiers
  83,11,Those who lie/deny/falsify with the Judgment Day/Resurrection Day
  83,12,"And none lies/denies/falsifiers with it except every/each transgressor/violator , sinner/criminal"
  83,13,"When/if Our verses/evidences are read/recited on him he said: \"The first`s/beginner`s myths/baseless stories"
  83,14,"No but, rather (it) dominated/overwhelmed on their hearts/minds , what they were gaining/acquiring"
  83,15,"No but, that they truly are from their Lord (on) that day being prevented (E)"
  83,16,Then that they truly are entering into the fire/roasting (E) the Hell
  83,17,"Then (it) will be said: \"That (is) what you were with it lying/denying/falsifying"
  83,18,"No but, that truly the righteous`/charitable` Book/judgment (is) in (E) Eley`yeen/height/elevation"
  83,19,And what made you know/informed you what (is) Eley`yoon/highest places
  83,20,A written/branded/inscribed Book
  83,21,The neared/closer witness it
  83,22,That truly the righteous/charitable (are) in (E) blessing/goodness
  83,23,On the luxurious beds/couches they look/watch
  83,24,You know in their faces/fronts the blessing`s/goodness` beauty and goodness (brightness)
  83,25,They are being given water/drink from sealed/completed pure nectar
  83,26,"Its end/conclusion (is) musk/fragrance, and in (for) that so the competitors/rivals should compete/rival"
  83,27,And its mixture/blend (is) from paradises` valuable water
  83,28,"A water spring/well, the neared/closer drink by (near) it"
  83,29,That truly those who committed crimes/sins were laughing/wondering from (about) those who believed
  83,30,"And when/if they passed by them, they signal/wink to each other"
  83,31,"And when/if they returned to their people/family , they returned enjoying/humorous"
  83,32,"And when/if they saw them they said: \"That truly, those are misguided (E)"
  83,33,And they were not sent on them protecting/observing
  83,34,So the day/today those who believed are laughing/wondering from (about) the disbelievers
  83,35,On the luxurious beds/couches they (are) looking/watching
  83,36,Did the disbelievers become rewarded/replaced what they were making/doing